  "fullText": [
    [
      { "text": "Now look " },
      { "text": "slowly", "blockId": "slowly" },
      { "text": " around you, and practice applying this idea " },
      { "text": "very specifically", "blockId": "specifically" },
      { "text": " to " },
      { "text": "whatever you see", "blockId": "whatever" },
      { "text": ":" }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "This table does not mean anything." }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "This chair does not mean anything." }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "This hand does not mean anything.", "blockId": "hand" }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "This pencil does not mean anything." }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "This body does not mean anything.", "blockId": "body" }
    ],
    [
      { "divider": true }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "Then look farther away from your immediate area, and apply the idea to a wider range of subjects:" }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "That door does not mean anything." }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "That face does not mean anything.", "blockId": "face" }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "That light does not mean anything." }
    ],
    [
      { "divider": true }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "The exercises " },
      { "text": "should not become ritualistic", "blockId": "ritual" },
      { "text": ", and care should be taken not to allow them to be so. The application of the idea is what is important. " },
      { "text": "Do not concentrate on the words themselves.", "blockId": "words" }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "The exercises " },
      { "text": "are not arranged in any order", "blockId": "order" },
      { "text": ", and " },
      { "text": "no allowance should be made for differences", "blockId": "differences" },
      { "text": " in the nature of the things to which they are applied. " },
      { "text": "That is the whole point of the exercises.", "blockId": "point" }
    ],
    [
      { "divider": true }
    ],
    [
      { "text": "A comfortable sense of leisure is essential.", "blockId": "leisure" }
    ]
  ]
}
